permafrost.tundra.mime

Class ImmutableMimeType

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.activation.MimeType
      • permafrost.tundra.mime.ImmutableMimeType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<javax.activation.MimeType>

    public class ImmutableMimeType
extends javax.activation.MimeType
implements java.lang.Comparable<javax.activation.MimeType>
    A subclass of MimeType that is immutable and supports comparisons and equality checks based on MimeType.match, which allows this class to be used as keys in a Map.
    See Also:
